Package de.hu.gralog.beans.propertyeditor Description

This package defines all PropertyEditors that are currently available in GrALoG.

PropertyEditors provide renderers and editors to GrALoG that are shown to the user when editing the corresponding properties. GrALoG is fully compatible to PropertyEditor conventions and also provides an Extension to PropertyEditor that allows to specify Components as renderers PropertyEditorRendererExtension.
